unity in your corner.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow\">\n<ul class=\"is-style-links-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://learn.wordpress.org/\">Learn with WordPress ↗&#65038;</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/\">Find support ↗&#65038;</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.wordpress.org/\">Dig into the code ↗&#65038;</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pro/wordpress/\">Meet local WordPress users ↗&#65038;</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-blueberry-1-color has-light-grey-2-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-elements-5ab64866da90390d7dd8ca15663284a3 is-layout-constrained\" id=\"community\" style=\"padding-right:0;padding-bottom:100px;padding-left:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light\" style=\"margin-bottom:60px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;min-height:500px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-0 has-background-dim\"></span><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2642\" height=\"997\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-12467\" alt=\"A black and white bird’s eye view of the thousands of contributors who attended WordCamp Europe 2022. They are all standing in front of the venue with their hands up in celebration.\" src=\"https://wordpress.org/files/2022/10/community-photo-2-q50-unscaled.webp\" style=\"object-position:50% 100%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"50% 100%\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2022/10/community-photo-2-q50-unscaled.webp?w=2642&amp;ssl=1 2642w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2022/10/community-photo-2-q50-unscaled.webp?resize=300%2C113&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2022/10/community-photo-2-q50-unscaled.webp?resize=1024%2C386&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/files/2022/10/community-photo-2-q50-unscaled.